SIMPLE: whitener
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whitener
<hw>Whit"en*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, whitens; a bleaching agent; a bleach; a bleacher; a
blancher; a whitewasher.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A chemical used as an adjunct to laundering white
cloth, which makes white cloth appear whiter. A bluing agent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whiteness</ent>⟦br⟧
